/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-ui-documentation_Result/260413_1358_Pre_ENH_21/cache/doxygen_json/dali-ui/xml/classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AsyncImageLoader.xml:433:<para>If the handle points to an <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AsyncImageLoader" kindref="compound">AsyncImageLoader</ref> object, the downcast produces a valid handle. If not, the returned handle is left uninitialized.</para>
