/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-ui-documentation_Result/260413_1358_Pre_ENH_21/cache/doxygen_json/dali-ui/xml/classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl.xml:275:<para>If handle points to a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl" kindref="compound">ImageUrl</ref> object the downcast produces valid handle. If not the returned handle is left uninitialized.</para>
