/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-ui-documentation_Result/260413_1358_Pre_ENH_21/cache/doxygen_json/dali-ui/xml/classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AsyncImageLoader.xml:458:<para>To keep track of the loading images, each load call is assigned an ID (which is returned by the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1AsyncImageLoader_1a4d94e94fd7ec4dede82bc499a2c5afe7" kindref="member">Load()</ref> call). To know when the Load has completed, connect to the ImageLoadedSignal. This signal should be connected before Load is called (in case the signal is emitted immediately).</para>
