/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-ui-documentation_Result/260408_1150_ENH-14_API_할루시네이션_제어_완료/cache/doxygen_json/dali-ui/xml/classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl.xml:299:<para>An instance of <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl" kindref="compound">ImageUrl</ref> can be created from <ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrlUtils_1aaff549725b670f5fa5f3cceae3f2b2ee" kindref="member">ImageUrlUtils::GenerateUrl()</ref>. Application can get url from <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl" kindref="compound">ImageUrl</ref>. When application does not use this anymore, the destructor of the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1ImageUrl" kindref="compound">ImageUrl</ref> is called. At this time, the buffer is deleted from the texture manager. <simplesect kind="note"><para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Visual" kindref="compound">Visual</ref> also have reference of the buffer. In this case, buffer will be deleted after visual is deleted. </para>
